as for more advanced users to gain exposure to each other's techniques and
work methods. Articles span a wide range of topics including patterns for
using the STL and Rcpp sugar functions, benchmarking & performance
concerns, and using Armadillo and the GSL. Each article includes a link to
full source code that can be run immediately using sourceCpp().

